snippet: An Iranian naval officer said a number of warships had been ordered to approach U.S. maritime borders as a response to the stationing of U.S. vessels in the Gulf, the semi-official Fars news agency reported on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Iran Says Warships Sailing Towards U.S.: Agency
headline.main: Iran Says Warships Sailing Towards U.S.: Agency

lead_paragraph: An Iranian naval officer said a number of warships had been ordered to approach U.S. maritime borders as a response to the stationing of U.S. vessels in the Gulf, the semi-official Fars news agency reported on Saturday.
